summary: I created this tower for my own use, and I decided to share.  I appreciate feedback.
descriptionHtml:
This is my tower just around the corner from Bloated Man\'s Grotto.

Features:
====================
726 Book Slots
29 Mannequins
17 Weapon Plaques
12 Dagger Displays
7 Weapon Displays
48 Vertical Weapon Racks
Private Garden w/ fish and insects
Temple with Shrines and Stones
2 Merchants
Teleports to all \'Nilla Houses plus Archmage Quarters, Thieves Guild, Jorrvaskr, and Dawnstar Sanctuary.

Full Crafting Equipment:
====================
Enchanting Station
Alchemy Station
Skyforge
Smelter
Grinding Wheel
Tanning Rack
Workbench
Cooking Spit

Note:
====================
I use the Sexy Riften 2.0 mod, so your textures may look different than the screenshots.
I highly recommend Unlimited Bookshelves by da5id2701: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10891

Known Issues:
====================
None
author: Ogdar
